Package: ljmds
Type: Package
Title: Local Jaccard MDS for Longitudinal Binary Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Kenichi", "Satoh",
    email = "kenichi-satoh@biwako.shiga-u.ac.jp",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4436-9347"))
Author: Kenichi Satoh [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4436-9347>)
Maintainer: Kenichi Satoh <kenichi-satoh@biwako.shiga-u.ac.jp>
Description: Visualisation of longitudinal binary data (a
    time-by-attribute matrix of 0/1 values) by a locally weighted
    Jaccard distance, multidimensional scaling with sequential
    modification in the sense of Mizuta (2003), Ward clustering on
    a trajectory distance, and a functional Rousseeuw silhouette
    criterion for joint selection of bandwidth and class number.
    Includes two example corpora (Peace Declaration of Hiroshima
    1947-2025 and US Presidential Inaugural Addresses 1789-2021),
    supplied as binary CSV matrices that contain no source text.
